This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and classification of Wikipedia articles, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning models for classification, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
